                <h2 id="phase1">Phase 1: Signal Detection (The Macro)</h2>
                <p>We began by ingesting the client's entire digital footprint‚ÄîLinkedIn, Google Site, and raw biography. The signal was immediately clear: <strong>High-Performance Individual</strong>.</p>
                
