                        <li><strong>Service:</strong> Deep, long-term commitment (Guide Dogs, Youth Corps, Secondary School Projects).</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <p><strong>The Strategy:</strong> Instead of a standard portfolio, we treated this as a <strong>Pre-Professional Brand Launch</strong>. The target was specific: NUS Merit Scholarship & Law School. The narrative needed to move from "I did this" to "This is who I am."</p>

                <h2 id="phase2">Phase 2: Structural Mapping (The Horizons)</h2>
                <p>We mapped the site architecture to answer three temporal questions. This ensures the portfolio is a vector, not a static point.</p>

